      <param name="UPDATEVIEW" displayname="Update View" type="Optional" direction="Output">
        <dialogReference>&lt;p&gt;Update View&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boolean&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Default: 1&lt;/p&gt;</dialogReference>
      </param>
    </parameters>
    <summary>This tool implements the K-Means cluster analysis for grids in two variants, iterative minimum distance (Forgy 1965) and hill climbing (Rubin 1967). </summary>
  </tool>
